         I‚Å¢B‚Å¢M‚Å¢1
         (Section
         4.1
         ).
Lines 4-1 and 4-2 update the weights in each layer following a given objective (Sections
         4.1
         and
         4.2
         ).
Note that
         Œ∏F‚Å¢Et
